title: NFT Finance will launch the governance token $NFTF and issued retroactive airdrop rewards to ENS holders
body:
NFT Finance will airdrop to ENS holders according to the $ENS airdrop rules. The Ethereum blocks snapshot 13656754.

The total amount of governance tokens $NFTF is 100 million, including 15% of early investors, 5% of team members, 55% of community treasury, and 25% of retroactive airdrops. 

$NFTF will be minted after the community proposal is passed. Stay tuned.
